data.description: Introducing an exceptional investment opportunity in the heart of Columbia City, Seattle! Featuring a charming home with 2 bedrooms/1 bathroom, situated on a spacious lot spanning 13,680 sqft. What makes this property truly exciting is its potential for multiple unit development. With the ability to build additional units, the possibilities are endless.    This property offers easy access to the light rail, shopping centers, restaurants, and the beautiful Lake Washington. Columbia City's vibrant atmosphere and diverse community make it a prime destination for residents and investors alike. Whether you're looking to expand your portfolio or design your dream development, this property provides the perfect canvas for your vision.
